snippet.title: Nightingale Realmwalker's Journey Trailer | The Game Awards 2022
snippet.description: Nightingale is an upcoming First person PVE crafting game, set in 1889. However, you're connecting to a magical network of portals, where you can explore unknown areas filled with eldritch creatures and fantastical beasts. Also, Mary Poppins umbrellas! There's no set release date for Nightingale as of yet.
